## Third-Party Components

This software includes the following third-party components:

### 7-Zip

This application bundles 7-Zip command-line binaries as an embedded extraction tool.

- Website: https://www.7-zip.org/
- License: GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL)
- Usage: Used solely for archive extraction (7z, rar). No RAR compression capability is provided.

The unRAR source code included in 7-Zip is subject to the following restriction:
- The unRAR sources cannot be used to re-create the RAR compression algorithm.

For full license details, see: https://www.7-zip.org/license.txt

For third-party notices specific to this project, see: docs/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md
